From 45ebf06c4adb2c3d4297f88b47ea2e2d84fd587d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Hiren Mehta <hiren.mehta@amd.com>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 17:16:48 -0700
Subject: arm64/dts/amd Add missing elba/giglio DTS files

Add PSCI, flash128, and secure DTS variants for Elba and Giglio SoCs.
Also refactors elba-16core.dtsi into separate PSCI and spin-table
includes, and adds flash128 partition layout support.

Signed-off-by: Hiren Mehta <hiren.mehta@amd.com>
---
